        "name": "Scylla Mobile - Outlet Management Enhancement",
        "description": "Collection untuk testing fitur Outlet Management berdasarkan docs 'Add Outlet & Manage Outlet_BE.md'. Mencakup Upload File, Create Outlet (with file_url), Outlet List, dan Remove Outlet.",
